      • executeScript

        public CompletableFuture<List<Object>> executeScript(String scriptResourcePath)
                                              throws Exception
        Execute a local script in the Tarantool instance. The path must be classpath-relative. `dofile()` function is executed internally, so possible exceptions will be caught as the client exceptions.
        Parameters:
        scriptResourcePath - the classpath resource path to a script
        Returns:
        script execution result
        Throws:
        Exception - if failed to connect to the instance or execution fails
